    <main id="conteudo"><section class="page-hero"><div class="wrap page-hero-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow"><span class="signal"></span>Electric mobility features</p><h1>Everything that helps you arrive, charge and move on.</h1><p>See how VeVolt organizes available data and community contributions in a clear experience for EV drivers.</p>
  </div></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="wrap"><div class="feature-split">
    <div class="feature-copy"><p class="kicker">01</p><h2>Nearby chargers</h2><p>Explore charging locations on the map and check distance, connectors, power, status and tariffs when available.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/testers">Join the test &rarr;</a></div>
    <picture class="app-phone">
    <source type="image/webp" srcset="/assets/app/en-map-360.webp 360w, /assets/app/en-map-720.webp 720w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 86vw, 320px">
    <img src="/assets/app-en-map.png" width="1080" height="2400" alt="Nearby chargers" loading="eager" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high">
  </picture>
  </div><div class="feature-split reverse">
    <div class="feature-copy"><p class="kicker">02</p><h2>VeVolt Community</h2><p>Confirm whether a charger worked and report prices, queues, faults or access issues. Review reports, photos, ratings and reliability.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/testers">Join the test &rarr;</a></div>
    <picture class="app-phone">
    <source type="image/webp" srcset="/assets/app/en-community-360.webp 360w, /assets/app/en-community-720.webp 720w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 86vw, 320px">
    <img src="/assets/app-en-community.png" width="1080" height="2400" alt="VeVolt Community" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
  </picture>
  </div><div class="feature-split">
    <div class="feature-copy"><p class="kicker">03</p><h2>Routes and range</h2><p>Keep your location as origin, choose a destination and estimate battery and range. Premium Safe Route adds compatibility, reliability and nearby alternatives.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/testers">Join the test &rarr;</a></div>
    <picture class="app-phone">
    <source type="image/webp" srcset="/assets/app/en-route-360.webp 360w, /assets/app/en-route-720.webp 720w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 86vw, 320px">
    <img src="/assets/app-en-route.png" width="1080" height="2400" alt="Routes and range" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
  </picture>
  </div><div class="feature-split reverse">
    <div class="feature-copy"><p class="kicker">04</p><h2>Costs on your device</h2><p>Record energy and amount paid, review history and compare charging with fuel. Personal records remain on your device.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/testers">Join the test &rarr;</a></div>
    <picture class="app-phone">
    <source type="image/webp" srcset="/assets/app/en-economy-360.webp 360w, /assets/app/en-economy-720.webp 720w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 86vw, 320px">
    <img src="/assets/app-en-economy.png" width="1080" height="2400" alt="Costs on your device" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
  </picture>
  </div><div class="feature-split">
    <div class="feature-copy"><p class="kicker">05</p><h2>VeVolt Market</h2><p>Find dealerships, repair shops, parts and rentals. Search by location or postal code and open external contacts, routes and reviews.</p><a class="text-link" href="/en/testers">Join the test &rarr;</a></div>
    <picture class="app-phone">
    <source type="image/webp" srcset="/assets/app/en-market-360.webp 360w, /assets/app/en-market-720.webp 720w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 86vw, 320px">
    <img src="/assets/app-en-market.png" width="1080" height="2400" alt="VeVolt Market" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
  </picture>
  </div></div></section>
